{"tid":1768424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多區和你lunch 籲周日遊行","createTime":"2019-12-04T05:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:05:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf754ccb17812608f043258d19b51509587b8f95","tid":1768424,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191204/EL3RTXDI6HC5Z7MIP2LV222L6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191204%2FEL3RTXDI6HC5Z7MIP2LV222L6E%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=5754ee46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191204%2FEL3RTXDI6HC5Z7MIP2LV222L6E%2F&h=b1c591aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191204/EL3RTXDI6HC5Z7MIP2LV222L6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n多區和你lunch 籲周日遊行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《香港人權與民主法案》通過後，多區打工仔繼續毋忘初心「和你lunch」，其中葵涌、觀塘、長沙灣及中環昨午分別繼續有網民自發集會，數以百計打工仔騰出午飯時間，以雙腳表達「五大訴求 缺一不可」的期盼，他們又呼籲公眾參與下周日的民陣國際人權日遊行。<br />\n<br />\n中午約12時45分，葵涌約20多人開始「和你lunch」，他們於九龍貿易中心外集合，沿途叫口號：「光復香港，時代革命。」附近的工廠大廈有人將樽狀物品扔下，幸無傷人。約1時，中環天橋亦有上百人張貼文宣，有參加者舉起「史上最恐怖的被捕儀式」文宣，抗議早前有示威者被捕時，大聲叫出自己的個人資料，以便家人律師可以在警署找到自己，但卻被警方掩蓋口部等方法，企圖阻止被捕者叫出自己個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191204/large/1575388588_2e70.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575388588_2e70.gif&h=6a5c9889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【葵 涌】昨午大批打工仔在葵涌參與和你lunch，高呼：「光復香港，時代革命。」。 許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191204/large/1575388587_4ba3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575388587_4ba3.gif&h=c882a399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【葵 涌】部份參與者在九龍貿易中心外手持Pepe蛙聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191204/large/1575388588_cd64.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575388588_cd64.gif&h=af9febea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中 環】中環天橋上不少市民高舉五隻手指，象徵五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不明液體襲觀塘無人傷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大膽敢言 多次唱淡大市<br />\n<br />\n幾乎同一時間，長沙灣有數十人豎起五隻手指象徵五大訴求，高叫口號：「五大訴求，缺一不可。」部份人高舉用A4紙印刷的文宣，又呼籲市民「12.8維園見」，防暴警員在旁戒備。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭至晚上繼續，網民發起在觀塘順利商場舉行「和你唱」，逾百人參與。有居民一度與參加者對罵，並投擲不明液體，但未有擲中任何人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張雅婷"},{"pid":"c0ac7e661ada6b4e0a8e83562e0c5f7584140b57","tid":1768424,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"100萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}